<div class="contributor-name" id="chunk-710312"><a href="https://mzalendo.com/mps-performance/national-assembly/13th-parliament/anthony-kimani-ichungwah/">Hon. Kimani Ichung’wah (Kikuyu, UDA)</a></div>
