<div class="contributor-name" id="chunk-710548">The Temporary Speaker (Hon. Omboko Milemba)</div>
<div class="speech-content">
<p>Thank you, Hon. Member. Most of those teachers are P1 teachers. Some of them are almost reaching retirement age. We also have 20,000 on internship.</p>
<p>Let us now hear from Hon. Didmus Barasa.</p>
